    r <- x %>%

                                              p < 0.05 ~ "*",
                                              p < 0.1 ~ ".", 
                                              TRUE ~ ""),
             res = paste0(Estimate, star)) %>%
      select(res)
    colnames(r) <- c(name(x))
    return(r)
  })
